## Troubleshooting

### Prayer Times Not Loading

1. Check your internet connection
2. Close and reopen the app
3. Pull down to refresh on the main screen
4. Without internet, the last cached data will be shown automatically

### Notifications Not Working

1. Go to iPhone Settings → Notifications → Ezan Vakti Lite
2. Make sure notifications are allowed
3. Check that the bell icon for the relevant prayer is green in the app
4. Restart your phone

### Location Not Found

1. Go to iPhone Settings → Privacy → Location Services
2. Set Ezan Vakti Lite to "While Using the App"
3. Make sure you have a good GPS signal
4. You can always select your city/district manually

### Qibla Compass Inaccurate

1. Calibrate by moving your phone in a figure-8 motion on a flat surface
2. Stay away from metal surfaces and magnets
3. Results are more accurate outdoors

### Verse of the Day Audio Not Playing

1. Check your phone volume (make sure it's not on silent)
2. Check your internet connection (audio is streamed online)
3. Close and reopen the app

